[49m[39m  400, 400[0m:[39m[49m - Sudden life events (hospitalization, family emergency, job loss) that aren't captured in historical patterns.
[0m[49m[39m  401, 401[0m:[39m[49m - Patients who always confirm but still no-show. Confirmation behavior and actual attendance aren't perfectly correlated.
[0m[49m[39m  402, 402[0m:[39m[49m - Seasonal shifts (holiday weeks, school breaks) that don't appear in the training window.
[0m[49m[39m  403, 403[0m:[39m[49m - Practice changes (new provider, new location, new hours) that invalidate historical patterns.
